00:00:15.730 --> 00:00:19.890
Edward Lewis, is a high-powered corporate
raider from New York, he buys and dismantles

00:00:19.890 --> 00:00:24.839
struggling companies, selling off the assets
for profit. He wants his girlfriend to accompany

00:00:24.839 --> 00:00:28.880
him during a business trip, but fed up with
being his "beck and call girl," she ends their

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:33.890
